{% block idPurp %}
This is the water mask for the InSAR products generated from a pair of Sentinel-1 {{ granule_type }} granules. Values of 0 indicate water, and pixels over land have a value of 1. It is an 8-bit unsigned integer GeoTIFF projected to {{ projection }}, and has a pixel spacing of {{ pixel_spacing|int }} m.
{% endblock %}
